    <description>Arm description: Subjects will be up titrated to liraglutide 3 mg QD and stay on that dose for the remainder of the 52-week drug intervention period.
Drug: Liraglutide 3 mg QD administered in a 6 mg/mL, 3 mL pen for subcutaneous injection.
