Drug: Liraglutide 3 mg placebo QD administered in a 6 mg/mL drug equivalent volumes, 3 mL pen for subcutaneous injection.
Dose escalation scheme: Initial dosage of a 0.6 mg drug equivalent volume per day, escalated bi-weekly by an 0.6 mg drug equivalent volume per day to a 3 mg drug equivalent volume per day over a total of 8 weeks.</description>
